Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:11.21,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an8}我說你 這裡不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:13.17,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an8}不對嗎 那這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:15.38,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an8}這裡更加不行啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大叔他意外地適合扮演父親的角色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他曾經就是一個父親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}尤力先生的妻子和女兒都去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}無論是人還是守墓者都會改變的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}世界真的很複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}複雜程度遠遠地超出我的想像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在笑什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你果然很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也到各處旅行過 就是沒看到有其他人像你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是不好的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等 這算不上回答…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你為我慶祝生日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本來就路況不佳 再加上視野又那麼差
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好壯觀的霧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說是壯觀不如說是讓人不快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她說少作抱怨快點前進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說 尤力先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼突然剎車了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總之先回車上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡霧很大 要是走散就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 尤力先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聲音消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們兩個沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剛才那是…打雷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}守墓者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}貴安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}貴安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}貴安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡是守墓者誕生處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是守墓者出生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們全都長得一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}守墓者就是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現確認同一個體的守墓者少則有數以百計 多則有數以千計人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}像「貝傑爾家族」和「蒂尼家族」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是研究者對同一類守墓者所作的命名和分類
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過 當然也有很多只被確認過一次的守墓者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈娜小姐無疑是屬於那一類的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來到一個不得了的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}疤面小姐是想回到自己出生的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也許是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好厲害 這反應是迄今為止最強烈的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}瑟利卡 是不是疤面就在附近？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們真的要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這前面都遍佈著守墓者誕生處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可是要回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蒂伊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只有不好的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會吧 我們都一起來到這裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不知道嗎 我可是很隨性的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蒂伊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你那是什麼表情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們往前走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟了 視野變得相當模糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我倒覺得已經很接近了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾 要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總之 一點點往前走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}尤力先生？艾利斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}瑟莉卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}尤力先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸…爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼要這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸…爸爸為何要把媽媽那最重要的夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我已經一頭霧水了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你 但這是媽媽的夢想也是媽媽的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好好記住 唯一能讓你活下去的一句話就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「想活下去」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}疤面小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們來接你了 疤面小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.41,0:20:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有這個必要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是在這裡出生的守墓者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說 如果疤面小姐想跟原來一樣作為守墓人活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也無法強行阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}尤力先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}疤面！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}瑟莉卡該如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就這麼跟瑟莉卡分開真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要讓那孩子靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要有那孩子在我就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}疤面！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行！我是守墓者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要作為守墓者助活人度過美好的人生…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大叔！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}疤面 守墓者是不會哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}瑟莉卡…瑟莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.91,0:21:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}疤面 今後就由我來保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:58.29,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\an3\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}終わらないメロディーを歌いだしました
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:58.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}吟唱起那支永無休止的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an1}你閉上嘴跟著我走就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.83,0:21:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an1}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an1}大叔還真不賴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:22:01.67,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\an3\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}とても大好きで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:22:01.67,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}它教人甚是歡喜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an1}這…這是表白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:05.55,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\an3\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}少し切なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:05.55,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}又教人黯然神傷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an1}少…少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an1}我也會全力保護你們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.09,0:22:06.97,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\an3\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.09,0:22:06.97,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}然而
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an1}做好心理準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:10.80,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\an3\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}止まることが出来なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:10.80,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}它卻又永無止息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an1}尤力先生好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:13.60,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\an3\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}嫌いになりました
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:13.60,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}遂讓我心生厭倦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an1}還真可靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:22.61,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\an3\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}たとえ大切な君のそばでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:22.61,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}哪怕偎依在所珍愛的你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:27.78,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\an3\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}Life on the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:27.78,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}這行星上的生靈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:32.91,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\an3\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}見える景色は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:32.91,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}所能看見的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an1}這麼說 那個小鎮叫什麼名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:38.67,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\an3\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}同じには出来ないのです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:38.67,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}也無法絲毫不差
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an1}歐斯提亞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:42.50,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\an3\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}心も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:42.50,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}無論心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an1}我們…我們三年四班被關在那個小鎮裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:46.34,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\an3\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}未来も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:46.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}還是未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:50.55,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\an3\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}笑顔も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:50.55,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)\1c&HFFFFFF\3c&H000000}或是笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:57.35,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)}そうまだ見ぬ愛も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:57.35,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)}和那未成型的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.39,0:23:01.27,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)}Sweet love in love world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.39,0:23:01.27,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)}慈愛的世界那甜蜜的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:05.28,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)}Sweet love in love world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:05.28,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)}慈愛的世界那甜蜜的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:08.82,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)}You know what you wanna be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:08.82,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(300,300)}你很清楚你自己的目標
